This patch shows how to modify `home.twig` to remove fixed heights from the
slideshow, adjust navigation spacing and add a class for the mobile
categories button. Apply these changes manually to your theme file.

    *** Begin Patch
    *** Update File: catalog/view/theme/default/template/common/home.twig
    @@
    -<div id="slideshow" class="swiper-container" style="min-height: 580px;">
    +<div id="slideshow" class="swiper-container">
    @@
    -<nav id="menu" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light mt-3">
    +<nav id="menu" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
    @@
    -<button class="btn btn-secondary d-md-none" id="category-button">Categories</button>
    +<button class="btn btn-secondary d-md-none btn-categories" id="category-button">Categories</button>
    *** End Patch